<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-550-792  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 550 792.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Newsbytes  August 15 1989* Full Text COPYRIGHT Newsbytes Inc. 1989.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Toolkit for laptop travellers.andO;</TITLE><AUTHOR>Endrijonas, Janet.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Computer Products Plus Inc. (product introduction).andO;Product:   Computer Products Plus Deluxe Road Warrior Toolkit (Tool kit)(product introduction)Computer Products Plus Road Warrior Toolkit (Tool kit) (productintroduction).andO;Topic:     Computer industryProduct IntroductionCommunications Equipment.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>TOOLKIT FOR LAPTOP TRAVELLERS HUNTINGTON BEACH, CALIFORNIA, 1989 AUG 11 (NB)-- Computer Products Plus (CP+) has recently released the Road Warrior andDelux Road Warrior Toolkits for travellers who run into problems hooking uptheir laptops to phone systems when they travel.andP;  In an interview withNewsbytes, Marketing Director Wendy Clifford explained that CP+ seeks toincrease the productivity of laptop computers and their users beyondtraditional limits by offering productivity enhancement accessories andreliable expert service.andP;  The toolkits will work with any laptop computeralthough they have been designed for the Toshiba line.andP;  The Toolkit is acompact travel pouch with all the necessary tools, adaptors and instructionsto hook up a modem to almost any US hotel or commercial phone system.andO;Clifford told Newsbytes that international versions are in the works.andP;  Thedetailed instructions that come with the kit include scenarios on severaltypes of connections ranging from a simple Y-connector to hooking alligatorclips under a wall plate.andP;  The kit even has a lighted magnifier for seeingphone connections in dark corners and behind hotel beds.andP;  The deluxe kitcontains the CP+ Connector that avoids the need for dedicated modem lineswhen connecting to a digital PBX phone system.andP;  A three minute installationallows the phone to be used for both voice and data.andP;  The Road WarriorToolkit lists for $49.95 while the Deluxe Road Warrior Kit sells for $139.95.andP;  CP+ Connectors are available separately for $99.00 each.andP;  (JanetEndrijonas/19890811/Press Contact: Jerry Kalman, Kalman Communications,213-829-5664)</TEXT></DOC>